<h2><strong>Holiday Inspirations</strong></h2>
<p>We’re here to make your 2020 summer holiday your most memorable experience so far. Begin the journey now by having a look around these summer treats and making a shortlist of places you’ve always pictured yourself. We’ve always said planning a trip should be just as fun as the trip itself.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Pick a place where you’ll love every minute, doing whatever you feel truly passionate about.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">If you want to give your boots a proper outing, Austria should absolutely be on the top of your list, but Slovenia and Germany are strong contenders too if you want somewhere a little different and off the beaten track.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><br />If scenery and adventure get you excited, try Norway or Iceland – they’re simply unlike anywhere else in the world. Every time we get a chance to visit, we take it. <br />France and Switzerland are perfect places for more summer playgrounds, or perhaps you could head even further to Canada for a unique, memorable experience.</p>
<h3><span>Any questions? Just ask</span></h3>
<p>Pick your favourite spot and we can give you recommendations and help you put together a trip that’s flexible for you.</p>
<p>We’re all different, so whether it’s activities, flight times, airports, accommodations or tours, we have 85 years of experience under our belt to help you out.</p>
<p>Of course that’s if you need it- we’re always here with ideas and tips that are just a quick call away. And don’t forget our incredible reps around the world that are on hand to answer any questions or offer any local knowledge on-location.</p>
<p>Whatever your choice, you can do it at your own pace, in your own time!</p>
<p><strong>Holidays built with your passions, local recommendations and reassurance at every step.</strong></p>
